Algorithm 2 iKDBA
1: procedure IKDBA(C,S, ν) 2: //C: a reference time series 3: //S: a set of time series 4: //maxIter: maximum number of iterations 5: //ν: the stiffness parameter of KDTW kernel 6: Ts A; //a D dimensional Timeseries 7: Double inertia = computeInertia(C, S); 8: Boolean Continue=True; 9: Int i = 0;
10: while Continue do 11: A=C; 12: C=KDTW-C2(C,S, ν); 13: Double new inertia = computeInertia(C, S); 14: if new inertia > inertia OR i > maxIter then 15: Continue = False;
16: i=i+1;
